   "source": "<ROUTINE LOST-IN-OCEAN-F (RARG)\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? .RARG ,M-LOOK>\n\t\t<TELL\n\"You are lost in the middle of the open ocean. There is no land in sight.\">\n\t\t<CLEVER-CONTENTS ,HERE \" Floating nearby\">\n\t\t<CRLF>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? .RARG ,M-BEG>\n\t\t<FUN-IN-OCEAN>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? .RARG ,M-END>\n\t\t<SOAK-IF-OPENED>)>>"
