   "source": "<ROUTINE EMERGE-AND-DROWN ()\n\t <COND (<NOT <EQUAL? ,CHANGED? ,GROUPER>>\n\t\t<JIGS-UP\n\"You have reemerged beneath the water. There is no air here.\nYou drown.\">)>>"
