   "source": "<ROUTINE OUBLIETTE-DOWN-EXIT ()\n\t <COND (,SMALL-FLAG \n\t\t<COND (,WATER-FLAG\n\t\t       <TELL \"The channel is frozen over.\" CR>\n\t\t       <RFALSE>)\n\t\t      (ELSE ,IN-CHANNEL)>)\n\t       (,WATER-FLAG\n\t\t<COND (<IN? ,WINNER ,ICEBERG>\n\t\t       <TELL ,YOU-HAVE-TO \" get in the water first\" ,PERIOD>)\n\t\t      (ELSE\n\t\t       <HOLD-BREATH>)>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (ELSE\n\t\t<TELL \"You'd never fit.\" CR>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
