   "source": "<ROUTINE EMPORIUM-EXIT ()\n\t <COND (<FSET? ,EMPORIUM-DOOR ,LOCKED>\n\t\t<THIS-IS-IT ,EMPORIUM-DOOR>\n\t\t<MERCHANT-AT-DOOR>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)\n\t       (<FSET? ,EMPORIUM-DOOR ,OPENBIT>\n\t        ,EMPORIUM)\n\t       (ELSE\n\t\t<TELL-OPEN-CLOSED ,EMPORIUM-DOOR>\n\t\t<RFALSE>)>>"
