   "endLine": 2294,
   "source": "<ROUTINE TELL-CUBE-COUNT (OBJ \"AUX\" CNT)\n\t <SET CNT <CUBE-COUNT .OBJ>>\n\t <COND (<ZERO? .CNT>\n\t\t<TELL \"no\">)\n\t       (ELSE <TELL N .CNT>)>\n\t <TELL \" cube\">\n\t <COND (<NOT <EQUAL? .CNT 1>>\n\t\t<TELL \"s\">)>\n\t <TELL \".\" CR>>"
