   "source": "<ROUTINE OCT-HOLE-DISAPPEARS ()\n\t <REMOVE ,OCTAGONAL-HOLE>\n\t <TELL\n\"You slide through the \" ,OCT-HOLE \", which constricts and disappears as\nsoon as you are through it.\" CR CR>>"
