   "endLine": 1619,
   "source": "<ROUTINE ONLY? (OBJ CON)\n\t <COND (<NOT <IN? .OBJ .CON>> <RFALSE>)\n\t       (<NOT <SET CON <FIRST? .CON>>> <RFALSE>)\n\t       (<NOT <EQUAL? .OBJ .CON>> <RFALSE>)\n\t       (<NEXT? .CON> <RFALSE>)\n\t       (ELSE <RTRUE>)>>"
