   "source": "<ROUTINE ICE-F ()\n\t <COND (<IN? ,ICEBERG ,HERE>\n\t\t<REDIRECT ,ICE ,ICEBERG>)\n\t       (<AND ,ICED-OBJECT <ACCESSIBLE? ,ICED-OBJECT>>\n\t\t<COND (<VERB? EXAMINE>\n\t\t       <TELL ,IT-LOOKS-LIKE \"an icy \" D ,ICED-OBJECT ,PERIOD>)\n\t\t      (<VERB? RUB>\n\t\t       <TELL \"It's cold.\" CR>)>)\n\t       (<NOT <EQUAL? ,HERE ,GLACIER-ROOM>>\n\t\t<TELL \"There is no ice here.\" CR>)>>"
