   "file": "interrupts.zil",
   "line": 682,
   "endLine": 696,
   "source": "<ROUTINE I-IDOL ()\n\t <QUEUE I-IDOL -1>\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,TEMPLE-ROOM>\n\t\t<TELL CR\n\"The idol is \">\n\t\t<COND (,IDOL-SLEEPED?\n\t\t       <TELL\n\"looking sleepy and tired.\">)\n\t\t      (ELSE\n\t\t       <TELL-IDOL-ACTION>\n\t\t       <TELL\n\" around the room, searching for something. No doubt\nit's you! It looks a little stiff, but for former basalt, it's pretty\nsupple.\">)>\n\t\t<CRLF>)>>"
