   "source": "<ROUTINE I-DOWNSTREAM (\"AUX\" (RM <>))\n\t <COND (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,IN-CHANNEL>\n\t\t<SET RM ,IN-PIPE>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,IN-PIPE>\n\t\t<SET RM ,IN-PIPE-2>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,IN-PIPE-2>\n\t\t<SET RM ,RUINED-PIPE>)\n\t       (<EQUAL? ,HERE ,RUINED-PIPE>\n\t\t<SET RM ,IN-SEWER>)>\n\t <COND (.RM\n\t\t<TELL CR\n\"The rushing water is forcing you downstream.\" CR CR>\n\t\t<GOTO .RM>)>>"
